physProgressList.reason: The estimated cost of construction as mentioned in Form-2 Engineer's Certificate is Rs. 115731000, however the promoter of the project is in advance stages of negotiation to lease the entire property to a retail chain. Because of the same according to the information and explanation given to us by the promoter, construction specifications have changed therefore reducing the estimated cost of construction. However, as there is no mechanism to alter the project cost mentioned in Form-2 Engineer's Certificate, the Engineer has mentioned the cost incurred for the project considering the original estimated cost of the project and physical completion of the project as at 28-02-2021. Accordingly, the construction cost incurred as mentioned by Engineer in Form-2 for the position as at 28-02-2021 is substantially higher than construction cost incurred and paid as per books of account.
